sentences.sentence: Copy the SQPLTRC executable into sqllib \ function \ unfenced.
sentences.translation: 将sqpltrc可执行文件复制到sqllib \ function \ unfenced中。

sentences.sentence: To resolve the problem, run UDF in an unfenced mode or reduce database Shared memory set to no more than 5 segments.
sentences.translation: 要解决这个问题，可以在unfenced模式下运行udf，或者将数据库共享内存减少至不多于5个段。
